        "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nJust two questios Jorge:\n1) Should we not have the implementation and configuration for the PAP-PDP topic(s) in policy-common/pdp rather than in drools-pdp, we should have a common implemntation of this for all PDPs.\n\n2) Should we have one or two topics? I think it would be better to have two: PAP-PDP for PAP to PDP communication and PDP-PAP for PDP to PAP configuration (names not important)",
